layout.text: Biologic Hemp was established in Denver, Colorado in 2016. We offer a variety of wholesale hemp cannabis extract based CBD, CBG, CBN, CBC & Delta 8 THC products manufactured & processed from industrial bulk hemp flower at large scale quantities.
